{
  "stem": "23645.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because they said, we're going to take you to another camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So some thought, maybe there's a better chance to go to another camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the rumor was that the camp is set up full of dynamite, and they're going to explode the-- the camp with the prisoners in it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't want to-- the Allies to discover all the horrors that they had committed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I remember lying on the floor with Chopnik, and let's escape.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we knew that very few ever escaped successfully.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Machine gun flying overhead, and we're lying down there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they  said, well, maybe we'll be liberated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Like hell we're going to get liberated.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's going to explode.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We're not going to make it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "What would have happened had you tried to escape and you'd have been caught?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- we might have-- we would have been killed instantly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The decision was made for us, because there was suddenly a hush that came over the camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 13 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, so here we were, Chopnik, and I, and trying to make up our mind.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Do we stick it out in here and chances of making it, or do we try and escape?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The decision was made for us, because all of a sudden there was dead silence, quiet.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The shelling stopped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Our block, Block 8, was close to the main gate, where we every day looked at it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was a clock there, and Arbeit macht frei.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "All these goodies were-- were there on the entrance.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember pulling myself and looking out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember the time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was 10 minutes to 4:00.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if you speak to Chopnik, he has a different kind of memories.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, each one remembers something differently.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
